Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.54,0:00:04.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku punya alasan tersendiri\Natas kepulanganku ke Jepang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.06,0:00:10.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini Ai pulang\Ndemi menikah dengan Nagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.78,0:00:11.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menikah?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.46,0:00:19.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai lega bisa mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.86,0:01:55.58,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kau pulang demi menikah denganku?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.72,0:01:57.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.08,0:01:58.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.36,0:02:04.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bolehkah aku beri jawaban\Nsaat kita berjumpa lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu berlebihan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.38,0:02:09.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa jadi begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu saja yang ingin kusampaikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai sudah puas sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku permisi pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.78,0:02:23.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu tadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu berarti...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hasil pertimbangannya selama tujuh tahun,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,berujung pada "pernikahan", ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia belum berubah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terdengar seperti Ai.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku juga harus menjawab.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau mengejarnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ajaran keluarga Umino:
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Ketulusan harus\Ndibalas dengan ketulusan!"
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu aku, Ai!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.06,0:02:51.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin beri jawaban.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah mengingatkanku\Nselama tujuh tahun ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.28,0:03:08.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang ini ada orang lain yang kusukai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku juga punya tunangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ditambah, adik tanpa hubungan darah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.80,0:03:24.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, tunggu...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu reaksimu meski\Nmenyukaiku selama 7 tahun,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,bahkan sampai berniat menikahiku?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.03,0:03:34.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau di luar dugaanku,\Ntapi aku tidak masalah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.98,0:03:37.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dipikir...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai dulu juga seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku dulu menyukainya\Nkarena sifatnya ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai sekarang, aku akan beralih haluan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa kau antar Ai pulang sampai ke rumah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.90,0:04:04.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia ingin jaga hubungan\Nsebagai teman masa kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu perkara mudah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.50,0:04:14.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak usah terburu-buru begitu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.84,0:04:17.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini karena
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai merasa malu kalau pulang diantar Nagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak paham, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.14,0:04:26.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak, lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini saja kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong tatap matanya Ai.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jangan tatap!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi berdebar begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sendiri yang suruh!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.12,0:04:56.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tampaknya sorotan matamu\Njauh lebih kuat sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf soal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.28,0:05:00.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, bukankah ada yang janggal?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, ini misi terakhirmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita mampir ke toko jajanan\Nyang penuh kenangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bikin kangen, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita dulu sering ke situ, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi pergi berdua dengan Nagi\Nkedengaran seperti kencan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi merasa gugup.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kau yang mengajakku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang sudah jadi minimarket, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak kapan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Nagi, apa kau masih ingat?\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bola karetku yang tersayang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.76,0:05:46.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu hadiah utama undian\Ndi toko jajanan yang Ai dulu incar!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Yang tersayang?"
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu ungkapan untuk hal\Nyang amat kau cintai.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.82,0:05:59.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai akan mempertaruhkan hidupku\Ndemi mendapatkan bola karet itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak dapat lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan menyerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok akan kucoba lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.86,0:06:14.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.30,0:06:21.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari segi probabilitas, aku bisa\Nmendapatkannya dalam waktu dekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi uang sakuku bulan ini habis.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.62,0:06:25.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minggu depan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah tidak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.30,0:06:35.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadiah utamanya, kemarin ada yang dapat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Undian butuh keberuntungan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menyerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Ai. Jangan menangis!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku tidak menangis!\N- Menangis gitu, kok!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu pernah kejadian begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa kau sudah paham apa yang kumaksud?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.92,0:07:07.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.66,0:07:11.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyerah mendapatkan bola karet\Nsetelah sekitar satu bulan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kali ini, sudah 7 tahun lamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih lagi,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.76,0:07:19.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai sudah berbeda dengan Ai yang dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini akan benar-benar kudapatkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi-ku yang tersayang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksud "beralih haluan" tadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,begitu ternyata?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa Nagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru pulang setelah sekian lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak makan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.30,0:07:50.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa saat kau bertemu dengan Ai?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alasan kepulangannya Ai...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.32,0:08:03.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya demi menikah denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai yang bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.14,0:08:17.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersiaplah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.46,0:08:22.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.72,0:08:35.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kau punya tunangan,\Nmemang berengsek kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, kau salah paham!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau bantah, bantah dengan tinjumu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan bantahan!\NTapi pembelaan!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebanyakan belajar membuatmu lembek, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.26,0:09:00.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham apa yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi bereskan seperti semula.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ajaran keluarga Umino:
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Dengarkan apa perkataan ibu!"
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah... dan satu lagi Nagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu tak ingat membesarkanmu
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.86,0:09:26.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi anak yang membuat orang lain menangis.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.60,0:09:31.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu benar,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu aku tak bisa berbuat apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kali ini aku harus menghadapinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu membuatku terpikir...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.68,0:09:47.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada empat orang?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.24,0:09:52.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.36,0:09:52.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan ini fase populerku?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak juga rasanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Nagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.02,0:10:06.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya hari ini\Naku keburu salah sangka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf sudah mengajak ribut.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.02,0:10:10.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kebiasaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hehe.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Sesekali bantu kerjaan sini!\N- Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.94,0:10:18.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lama sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mampir ke rumah dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.24,0:10:23.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.16,0:10:24.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku perlu bicara denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang tiba-tiba kau lakukan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini parah, tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menyukai Hiro,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi berniat menikahi Ai?\NApa maumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.50,0:10:51.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak menyangka tunanganku itu\Ntukang nembak dan mengibul soal nikah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan diam saja, katakan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benar-benar minta maaf...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.80,0:11:08.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lipat itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau suka Ai tapi itu dulu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, sekarang kau benci dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.10,0:11:20.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau malah kau menyukai\NHiro dan Ai secara bersamaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.60,0:11:26.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan Amano, kau\Nbelum pernah suka sama seseorang?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.04,0:11:28.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pernah, kok!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Papa, Mama dan Sachi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku suka mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tidak dengan kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pantas saja tidak nyambung.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.18,0:11:37.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apaan coba?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.88,0:11:43.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama 17 tahun hidup,\Nbisa-bisanya tak pernah jatuh cinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.94,0:11:49.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau bagaimana lagi?\NSekolahku dari dulu khusus perempuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lawan ngobrolku selama ini\Ncuma om-om berdasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Bagaimana rasanya?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya menyukai seseorang...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa coba yang tanya begituan\Nke tunangannya...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah jawab saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di saat seperti apa kau merasa bahagia?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.82,0:12:10.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku makan masakan enak,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,menemukan pakaian yang bagus,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan dapat reaksi di media sosial.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahagianya 100 kali lipat dari itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perumpamaanmu seperti anak SD.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu supaya kau bisa paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.70,0:12:34.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau belum pernah melipat handuk, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Handuk selalu terlipat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir ini hotel?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.84,0:12:42.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi punya ide!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih belum selesai melipat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.28,0:12:52.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Indah, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kembang api?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.30,0:12:58.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat Hiro kemari, aku beli ini\Nkarena ingin main bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh menyesalkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Nagi memang aneh, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiba-tiba menghina?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.50,0:13:13.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis, Hiro dan Ai itu\Ntidak ada mirip-miripnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau menyukai mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu dan sekarang jelas beda, lah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mohon penjelasannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyukai Ai karena\Ndia tetangga dan dekat denganku,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,sedangkan Segawa karena\Ndia rivalku di sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku mengerti!\N- Apanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.80,0:13:34.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu berarti kau akan suka pada\Nsiapa pun yang mau bicara denganmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak segampang...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa menyangkal itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa bahas beginian dengan tunangan...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu berarti...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.10,0:13:48.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.78,0:13:54.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.38,0:13:59.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kemungkinan kau akan\Nsuka padaku suatu saat nanti?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.10,0:14:04.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mustahil juga, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahan dulu kembang apinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang bereskan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.14,0:14:15.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu kakak...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.68,0:14:22.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Juga ada kemungkinan akan suka padaku?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang disukai, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jatuh cinta itu ternyata bikin bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku bertemu kakakku...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaan seperti apa yang akan timbul?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahagianya 100 kali lipat dari itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa jadi Nagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasa senang saat bersama Nagi
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,menandakan kalau aku bahagia?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu berarti...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senang tidak selalu berarti bahagia, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti benar begitu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Erina.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pinjam baju ini, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau paling cantik sedunia!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.42,0:15:23.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi ke mana kok tiba-tiba?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai berdandan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku diajak oleh cowok sekelasku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.96,0:15:32.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.44,0:15:34.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku terlambat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-A-Apa maksudnya ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bakal ditembak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.52,0:15:52.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa Amano di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sendiri juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau adikku kenapa-kenapa bakal repot!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.24,0:15:58.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demikian pula aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.46,0:16:00.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada.\NCuma perasaanku saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,He-Hei...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan terlalu nempel!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahan dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi nanti tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahagianya 100 kali lipat dari itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi, ke sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penyamaran, sudah oke!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini norak sekali,\Nbukannya malah jadi mencolok?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.76,0:16:43.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang penting dia tidak mengenali kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.28,0:16:44.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.18,0:16:45.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.68,0:16:50.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak perlu sembunyi\Ndi tempat sempit lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia marah?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini yang sedang tren, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.86,0:16:58.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.46,0:17:07.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar Sachi,\Nkenapa kau senang dikasih begituan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan dia tipe yang disukai Sachi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barusan kau cemburu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma khawatir saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai kakak!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidakkah kau terlalu sayang adikmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.06,0:17:22.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Ayo pergi.\N- Ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak kapan suasananya jadi begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini baru muda masa!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pasti ditolak.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tukang nembak memang beda,\Nkenapa bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.28,0:17:43.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan panggil aku itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kalian berdua lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.94,0:17:49.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.70,0:17:51.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu kalian di situ.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebetulan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tidak sengaja lewat sini, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal mengikut dari awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketahuan, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu karena kau masih SMP tapi keluyuran.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah lewat jam enam, lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, kau tadi habis ditembak, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahun ujian, jangan cinta-cintaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.04,0:18:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matsuda itu murid paling pintar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu aku menerimanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menerima, katamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau tahu apa artinya itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.92,0:18:25.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak tidak rela kalau\Naku berpacaran dengan seseorang?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong apa kau ini?\NKau itu cuma adikku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.08,0:18:30.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.20,0:18:31.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, Sachi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku tidak rela?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin begitu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lampunya merah, lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.12,0:18:53.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.50,0:19:00.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Tarik napas panjang Haleluya,\Ndi manakah kau?♫
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.32,0:19:03.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Tarik napas panjang Haleluya,\Nbiar hati ini menyala♫
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Tak peduli meski terbakar hangus♫
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,♫Desir setrum...♫
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa ternyata jago nyanyi juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.70,0:19:17.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku suka lagu yang berjudul\N"Arus Pendek" ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya "Arus Pendek" lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.04,0:19:20.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku nyanyi lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi pertemuan dengan tunanganmu diundur?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.98,0:19:27.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rencananya setelah musim panas selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau tidak keberatan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada gunanya aku terus lari.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.30,0:19:36.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa saja dia ternyata orang baik-baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada benarnya juga, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.02,0:19:40.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi sekarang punya pacar?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ditanya rela atau tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tandanya kau sedang dites.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dites?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.60,0:19:54.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi intinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau tidak rela?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain,\Nkau sebenarnya tidak rela.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.90,0:20:03.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis, kalau adikmu bahagia\Nkarena punya pacar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harusnya ikut senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.00,0:20:16.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi anehnya, aku tidak merasa demikian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Langsung kutanya saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.98,0:20:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa bagimu Sachi adalah gadis yang menawan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau hanya adik yang kau sayang?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia adik tapi bukan adikmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.48,0:20:30.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan benar begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu kesimpulannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.76,0:20:39.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus menyiapkan makan malam\Njadi aku izin pulang!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.56,0:20:48.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sangat menggemaskan\Nkalau sedang kebingungan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini langsung tidur saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian sudah sedekat itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.44,0:21:05.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ditubruk dengan kuat,\Nsampai aku jatuh ditindih.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Dia jantan, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.98,0:21:10.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan, hentikan, hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awal pacaran sudah begitu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Diam kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hubunganmu dengan orang seperti itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan merestuinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.04,0:21:26.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami bahas anjing\Nyang ada di rumahnya Erika.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.98,0:21:30.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kadang aku minta dia beri makan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.28,0:21:31.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak kenapa coba?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ngotot banget bikin jijik.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi itu bukan soal pacarmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.32,0:21:37.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku bohong soal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.38,0:21:41.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menolaknya dengan halus dan hormat.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.34,0:21:44.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ha? Kenapa kau\Nmengaku menerimanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.48,0:21:46.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengetesmu karena kau menyebalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tes?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingin mati saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Nagi bagaimana makan malamnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.24,0:22:04.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata kakak tidak rela.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.30,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kalian satu rombongan.
